{"tid":29711,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得自己條命係撮合情侶咁...","createTime":"2016-12-08T17:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T04:15:14.000Z","uid":61318,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"823c9225ece1129fc17ca1706943b8ec10396b45","tid":29711,"uid":61318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"小弟今年19歲 覺得好灰<br />\n<br />\n鍾意過兩個女仔，第一個同佢無限接近，我亦都有意無意地對佢表示有好感，最後得到嘅結果就係佢成為咗人哋嘅女朋友 ，而家仲好恩愛<br />\n<br />\n第二個比較近期，一直都有同佢保持聯絡，係中學同學嚟，都同佢whatsapp咗一段時間，基本上咩都傾下咁，同樣地有意無意表示有好感，但因為前排我好多功課，完全無時間去理功學以外嘅嘢，到我搵返佢果陣 佢就話：我拍拖啦 趕得切聖誕節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經歷完兩次咁嘅事 發覺自己好似鍾意人嘅話 對方過無耐就會即刻有拖拍 覺得好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  果種心情真係好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878a5bd535f9f621c942ed65dacc8726148e2f92","tid":29711,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"算啦，命中注定你做一世毒撚"},{"pid":"a7f0633416fb3c45b32e3f65009f3b82a9940ffa","tid":29711,"uid":61318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦，命中注定你做一世毒撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經放棄 繼續頹落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b16b958fb4780dbea91bb08a8106e4093821364","tid":29711,"uid":61318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算啦，命中注定你做一世毒撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經放棄 準備繼續頹落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d3cfbbc9cf50aa5b5044713f1c72fd33fa12c50f","tid":29711,"uid":1923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:30:27.000Z","msg":"係創意台見到仲以為係潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween巴打你加油啦，可能真係巧合啫<br />\n19歲就頹，你注定一世毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b41f4c94ca815417fe88662d6c26ab3d43c4f3","tid":29711,"uid":737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:32:47.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣19歲 我好眀白個種感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b859d89d2387abfdd4c8d412bce5382db0a0bf1a","tid":29711,"uid":61318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:42:36.000Z","msg":"果種感覺難受之餘又好複雜 眼白白睇住佢哋離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ae2b7cdf39f69757ac3b92deeadadc0ff908d6","tid":29711,"uid":13444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T19:48:14.000Z","msg":"小小事就灰，而家既小朋友真係未見過風浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac67f65f565405ec6ff82c7eba77208c9855a621","tid":29711,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T19:59:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪開錯台啊on9仔"},{"pid":"924b94b92e7483cd6dfd3a5299a06977b9b8af7f","tid":29711,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"你覺得我點解改依個名？"},{"pid":"ea0df526687fa43a3c7b09c1ca4f010a48f15049","tid":29711,"uid":14091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得我點解改依個名？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062666d9b89010d649e9a5b70f4f65c6e0538975","tid":29711,"uid":61318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你覺得我點解改依個名？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\